                  <section ID="s32">
                     <id root="fd6cf7cc-7a3b-4af8-a81d-dc9cadd58db5"/>
                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <title>Storage recommendations:
</title>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">Before reconstitution:</content> Store at 20° to 25° C (68° to 77° F) (See USP controlled Room Temperature)
</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">Protect from light.</content> Retain in carton until time of use.
</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>
                           <content styleCode="bold">After reconstitution:</content> Product must be stored under refrigeration, between 2° to 8°C (36° to 46°F) and any unused portion should be discarded after 72 hours.
</paragraph>
                        <paragraph>This container closure is not made with natural rubber latex.
